@adamdriscoll We could extend RawUI in `TestHost` to write tests for `WriteProgress`. See [Read-Host.Tests.ps1](https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/blob/master/test/powershell/Modules/Microsoft.PowerShell.Utility/Read-Host.Tests.ps1) And it is likely that different tests are needed for different platforms.
Maybe @JamesWTruher comment this.

About binary cmdlets. You add `ProgressCharacter `  to public class `ProgressRecord` so binary cmdlets can use free the property.
